title: BTC Bull Run Incoming? Bitcoin Supply on Exchanges Hits Six-Year Low
description: Over the past week, the total supply of Bitcoin (BTC) held on centralized cryptocurrency exchanges dropped to a six-year low, according to CryptoQuant data, with exchanges having net outflows for 45 months in a row now.
